OL,4,Chimself at Centre of Islamic Studies
OL,6,FThe wing will host the 'King Charles
OL,7,FIII Programme', a new initiative to
OL,8,Fconsolidate key activities inspired by
OL,9,Fhis beliefs.
OL,11,FFounded in 1985, the centre evolution
OL,12,Fhas been closely followed by the King,
OL,13,Feven being granted a Royal Charter by
OL,14,Fhis mother, Queen Elizabeth II, in
OL,15,F2012.
