OL,3,CKing Charles opens wing named after
OL,4,Chimself at Centre of Islamic Studies
OL,6,FThe centre hosts a 'young Muslim
OL,7,FLeadership Programme,' as well as
OL,8,Fconferences focused on global issues
OL,9,Flike the environment and
OL,10,Fsustainability, both close to the
OL,11,FKing's heart.
OL,13,FAddressing the congregation, His
OL,14,FMajesty said, "In this milestone
OL,15,Fanniversary year, I can only say that
OL,16,Fit is with enormous pride and
OL,17,Fadmiration that I join you all here
OL,18,Ftoday to pay tribute to this
OL,19,Fremarkable centre.
