OL,6,F"The centre's ongoing commitment to
OL,7,Fobjective scholarship and
OL,8,Finternational co-operation,
OL,9,Funderpinned by principles of dialogue,
OL,10,Fdeep understanding and mutual respect,
OL,11,Fis more imperative than ever in
OL,12,Ftoday's world."
OL,14,FThe visit was rounded off with a
OL,15,Freception in the aptly named, King
OL,16,FCharles III Garden with a chance to
OL,17,Fmeet interfaith representatives,
OL,18,Facademics and trustees.
