OL,4,Chimself at Centre of Islamic Studies
OL,6,FThe King has a history with co-founder
OL,7,Fof the Oxford Centre for Islamic
OL,8,FStudies, Dr Farhan Ahmad Nizami, as
OL,9,Fthey first met when the king visited
OL,10,Fin 1993.
OL,12,FThe then-Prince of Wales gave a
OL,13,Fpassionate lecture at the Sheldonian
OL,14,FTheatre about the need for religious
OL,15,Ftolerance. Many saw it as a milestone
OL,16,Fin race relations.
