OL,3,CKing Charles opens wing named after
OL,4,Chimself at Centre of Islamic Studies
OL,6,FSpeaking in 1993, he said, "If there
OL,7,Fis much misunderstanding in the West
OL,8,Fabout the nature of Islam, there is
OL,9,Falso much ignorance about the debt our
OL,10,Fown culture and civilisation owe to
OL,11,Fthe Islamic world.
OL,13,F"It is a failure which stems, I think,
OL,14,Ffrom the straitjacket of history which
OL,15,Fwe have inherited."
OL,17,FSince then, the centre has found it
OL,18,Fimportant to work on the international
OL,19,Fstage to improve islamic relations.
