OL,6,FThe centre's director Dr. Farhan
OL,7,FNizami said, "That is why we need
OL,8,Fthese occasions more and more and that
OL,9,Fis why the relevance of the centre has
OL,10,Fincreased over time.
OL,12,F"There is now a bigger responsibility
OL,13,Fupon us but equally, this is a mark of
OL,14,Fthe importance of these times that
OL,15,Fneed to be addressed."
